title: Emotional victory for Tom Brady, Cowboys proving themselves, Cardinals still undefeated, MNF Preview
itunes:title: Emotional victory for Tom Brady, Cowboys proving themselves, Cardinals still undefeated, MNF Preview
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Michael Robinson dissect what was an emotional and victorious return to Foxborough for Tom Brady. Kyler Murray and the Cardinals are still undefeated while the Cowboys are proving they're a contender in the NFC. Nate Burleson gives his Game Ball to both NYC teams and will the Raiders feel like MNF is a home game in Los Angeles vs the Chargers?

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
